article.description: — Rocky Kreuser had 18 points and 14 rebounds to lift North Dakota State to a 68-54 win over Cal State Northridge on Friday night.
article.headline: Kreuser lifts North Dakota St. past CS Northridge 68-54
article.linkText: Kreuser lifts North Dakota St. past CS Northridge 68-54
article.story: FARGO, N.D. -- — Rocky Kreuser had 18 points and 14 rebounds to lift North Dakota State to a 68-54 win over Cal State Northridge on Friday night. Grant Nelson had 18 points for the Bison (6-4), who have won five consecutive home games. Tyree Eady added nine points and 12 rebounds. Onyi Eyisi had 19 points and seven rebounds for the Matadors (3-6). Atin Wright added 17 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
